{"lemma":"شَطُّ","slug":"شَطُّ","root":"ش.ط.ط","root_slug":"ش-ط-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ط-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22318","n22321"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go to extremes, to go too far, to exceed proper bounds, to be excessive"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deviate, to digress, to stray"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chott, bank, shore, coast, seashore, riverside, seaside, riverbank, seacoast, beach, strand","examples":[{"text":"شَطُّ الْعَرَبِ","english":"Shatt al-Arab"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22318","headword_ar":"شَطَّ","root":"$T","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) [the latter contr. to analogy,] the pret. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatala","text_ar":"قَتَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, [and the like is said in the TA,]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~N","text_ar":"شَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a house, or dwelling, S, Msb, TA, and a place of visitation, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, distant, remote,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far off."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a fiY Als~awomi","text_ar":"شَطَّ فِى السَّوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~u","text_ar":"شَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTN","text_ar":"شَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aT~a","text_ar":"اَشَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) or both, (Msb, K,) but the latter is the more common; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$tT~","text_ar":"اشتطّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beyond the due bounds, in offering a thing for sale and demanding a price for it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in bargaining for a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) the verb in this phrase is also followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) IB says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a","text_ar":"شَطَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEuda","text_ar":"بَعُدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, distant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: and that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aT~a","text_ar":"اَشَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboEada","text_ar":"اَبْعَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY TalabiY","text_ar":"فِى طَلَبِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aT~uwA","text_ar":"اَشَطُّوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They went far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to a great"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an extraordinary length, in seeking me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawomu fiY TalabinaA","text_ar":"القَوْمُ فِى طَلَبِنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aT~a","text_ar":"اَشَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men, sought us walking and riding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlmafaAzapi","text_ar":"فِى المَفَازَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$aT~a","text_ar":"اَشَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away in the desert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) as though he went far in it. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a fiY siloEatihi","text_ar":"شَطَّ فِى سِلْعَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTN","text_ar":"شَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exceeded the due bounds, and went far from what was right, in respect of his commodity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"article of merchandise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a fiY Hukomihi","text_ar":"شَطَّ فِى حُكْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) aor"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) only, (TA,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) the latter aor. is mentioned in the L, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTN","text_ar":"شَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) in the K, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTiyTN","text_ar":"شَطِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also; (Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$T~","text_ar":"اشطّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$tT~","text_ar":"اشتطّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlqaDiy~api","text_ar":"فِى القَضِيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$T~","text_ar":"اشطّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted unjustly, wrongfully, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his judging,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercising jurisdiction"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rule,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passing sentence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in judging,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTotu Ealayohi","text_ar":"شَطَطْتُ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oTaTotu","text_ar":"اَشْطَطْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I acted unjustly, wrongfully, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically, against him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned by A'Obeyd. (S, L.) It is said in the Kur [xxxviii. 21],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA ta$oTuTo","text_ar":"وَلَا تَشْطُطْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tu$oTiTo","text_ar":"تُشْطِطْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tu$aT~iTo","text_ar":"تُشَطِّطْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tu$aATiTo","text_ar":"تُشَاطِطْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different readings,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And go not thou far from what is right:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) all having this meaning: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceed not the due bounds."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTN","text_ar":"شَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceeding the due bounds"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, Mgh) in selling, and in demanding or seeking, and in exercising jurisdiction, &c., (AA,) or in everything. (S.) It is said in a trad."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahaA mahoru","text_ar":"لَهَا مَهْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivolihaA laA wakosa walaA $aTaTa","text_ar":"مِثْلِهَا لَا وَكْسَ وَلَا شَطَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She shall have the dowry of her like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there shall be no falling short nor exceeding."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And you say of a just sale,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA baxosa fiyhi walaA $aTaTa","text_ar":"لَا بَخْسَ فِيهِ وَلَا شَطَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bxs","text_ar":"بخس"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wlA","text_ar":"ولا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTa","text_ar":"شُطُوطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T and TA in that art.,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no deficiency in it nor excess."},{"kind":"text","text":"] You also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a","text_ar":"شَطَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Alqawoli","text_ar":"فِى القَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aTaTN","text_ar":"شَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was rough, harsh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarse, in speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a","text_ar":"شَطَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"used transitively, [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He passed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed beyond,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or, probably,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed far away from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a place. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~a fulaAnFA","text_ar":"شَطَّ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~N","text_ar":"شَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He distressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afflicted, such a one, and treated him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used him, unjustly, wrongfully, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) so say AZ and Aboo-Malik. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAT~ahu fa$aT~ahu","text_ar":"شَاطَّهُ فَشَطَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 3."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","L","AA","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n22321","headword_ar":"شَطٌّ","root":"$T","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a river: (S, Msb, K:) and of a valley: (S, Msb:) or, of the latter, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising ground next the bottom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uT~aAnN","text_ar":"شُطَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) the latter occurring in a verse, accord. to one relation; but"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1549},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to another relation, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uToA=nN","text_ar":"شُطْا=نٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aATiy^N","text_ar":"شَاطِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aT~N","text_ar":"شَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel's hump; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any side"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uTuwTN","text_ar":"شُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","AHn"]}]}}